\end_inset

 well estimate a real-valued probability measure
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 for every event, we call 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

 is in of the core of 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mu}$
\end_inset

.
 Formally, we have the following definition:
\end_layout

